ActFirst Nations Fiscal and Statistical Management Act
SubjectOrder Amending the Schedule to the First Nations Fiscal and Statistical Management Act.
PrecisOrder Amending the SCHEDULE TO THE FIRST NATIONS FISCAL AND STATISTICAL MANAGEMENT ACT by adding 4 First Nations, in order to allow them to participate in the property tax regime established by the FIRST NATIONS FISCAL AND STATISTICAL MANAGEMENT ACT.
